{"tid":680904,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"頑皮鬆獅犬卡窗邊半天吊險墮樓　暴曬句鐘中暑","createTime":"2018-05-27T14:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T11:07:36.000Z","uid":1221,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f383585cf73ee1a6dbfcabd413fd520509221cf2","tid":680904,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T14:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180527/photo/bkn-20180527133947099-0527_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180527173726\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180527%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180527133947099-0527_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180527173726&h=d7eb14c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上環皇后大道中328號中源中心低層一單位，一隻成年黃毛鬆獅犬，疑好奇或盼主人返家，憑窗望街，進而從窗口探出前半身，距料向下跌，猶幸後半身近雙腿被窗框卡住，未致墮樓，但卻半天吊掛在窗邊貼着外牆。 <br />\n<br />\n鬆獅犬進退不得，嗚咽哀叫，時值艷陽高掛，酷熱天氣警告持續，鬆獅犬因毛多，在暴曬下，辛苦難耐，但也只能可憐巴巴地帶着無奈的眼神待救，直至11時許，已接近中午時分，才被人發現，街坊見狀亦替鬆獅犬感到「好牙烟」，而且估計牠已暴曬至少一小時。 <br />\n<br />\n消防接報到場拯救，愛護動物協會亦獲通知到場協助，登門發現大門上鎖，屋內無人，正準備通知警方，再爆門進入時，狗主及時出現，開門讓消防員將鬆獅犬救離險境，救入屋內。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180527/photo/bkn-20180527133947099-0527_00822_001_03p.jpg?20180527173726\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180527%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180527133947099-0527_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20180527173726&h=56ce71e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n愛協人員發現鬆獅犬疑因過度暴曬而中暑，嚴重脫水，情況嚴重，於是將牠送往灣仔愛協總部救治狗主亦陪同前往。"},{"pid":"b16cedc0f59d337f078d1ab5c0d6f69135b0082e","tid":680904,"uid":73043,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T14:30:19.000Z","msg":"好心出街就關窗啦"},{"pid":"77c1e8df7e3b47c2335b04bbf59b314ff4e64d2b","tid":680904,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b16cedc0f59d337f078d1ab5c0d6f69135b0082e","tid":680904,"uid":73043,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T14:30:19.000Z","msg":"好心出街就關窗啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T23:18:12.000Z","msg":"其實會唔會係開少少等空氣流通，隻狗望吓推開曬，關曬一定熱死狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b36e51ace44103d1ff4d6f0cbe09d4753389a74","tid":680904,"uid":71391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T23:23:47.000Z","msg":"如果係人<br />\n<br />\n一定捱唔到咁耐"},{"pid":"d4612b10e8c09b7cd72d7bef448c4e09ada980f9","tid":680904,"uid":175888,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T23:55:04.000Z","msg":"我知隻狗好撚慘<br />\n但我一入個post見到張相就笑咗出聲"},{"pid":"eb1cef8b15a8597d190a7e67c75b0d2460c7d08c","tid":680904,"uid":19360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4612b10e8c09b7cd72d7bef448c4e09ada980f9","tid":680904,"uid":175888,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T23:55:04.000Z","msg":"我知隻狗好撚慘<br />\n但我一入個post見到張相就笑咗出聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T00:01:35.000Z","msg":"+1"},{"pid":"9e16dc7fa582fa7c423ad4df47f87f2cec673ac1","tid":680904,"uid":172306,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d4612b10e8c09b7cd72d7bef448c4e09ada980f9","tid":680904,"uid":175888,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T23:55:04.000Z","msg":"我知隻狗好撚慘<br />\n但我一入個post見到張相就笑咗出聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T00:19:25.000Z","msg":"因為真係好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c64e2755af7b53402763303041dc68c7f3b5c28","tid":680904,"uid":95196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T09:44:04.000Z","msg":"正常狗都唔會跳街..."},{"pid":"ee9c5835bb535cca375c052268b93e422bb47c8b","tid":680904,"uid":137627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T10:56:30.000Z","msg":"明知自己笨拙就唔好玩高難度野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba85867f191e15e3c2e169a246828f4bd2d216f9","tid":680904,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T11:06:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180527/photo/bkn-20180527133947099-0527_00822_001_03p.jpg?20180527173726\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180527%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180527133947099-0527_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20180527173726&h=46d62fc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢條咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27c9975113c05d313bcd2e8ad09dd7ddc742b85","tid":680904,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T11:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}